title: Vaccines do not cause autism, they save lives
description:
A new survey found 21% of millennials think vaccines cause autism. This isn't just wrong, it's dangerous. Vox's Dylan Matthews explains why vaccines are so important in 2 minutes. For more on the survey: http://www.vox.com/2015/1/31/7954725/vaccines-autism-young-adults
